histogram.summary:
Tracks the sharing actions executed when the sharing scenario was initiated
for a {EntryPoint}. To view how often this sharing scenario was triggered,
take a look at: Mobile.Share.EntryPoints. Currently only on iOS.

Android: Records the time it takes from ToS fragment attached to the
activity to the device ownership check completing.
{MobileFreInflationSpeedComparison}

Android: Records the time it takes from Lightweight FRE launch to the
enterprise policy check completing. This check is often skipped when its
result becomes irrelevant. {MobileFreInflationSpeedComparison}

Android: Records the time it takes from from Lightweight FRE launch to the
device ownership check completing. This check is often skipped when its
result becomes irrelevant. {MobileFreInflationSpeedComparison}
